name: Outburst
description:
"I keep blaming myself for every mistakes i did. My brain tried to correct the memory but the fact it doesn't change any of things. That's where my anxiety always rising. So tired"

Someone having an anxiety attack may have an "outburst" despite their best efforts to try and prevent this and shame themselves for hours (or even days) afterwards

Please be gentle, stay with them

Share to raise awareness
